@startuml sequence-water-delivery
title Water Delivery Registration Flow

actor User
participant WaterDeliveryController
participant WaterDeliveryService
participant SystemSettingsService
participant FamilyService
participant WaterDeliveryRepository

User -> WaterDeliveryController : POST /hf/water-deliveries(WaterDeliveryDTO)
WaterDeliveryController -> WaterDeliveryService : saveWaterDelivery(dto)
WaterDeliveryService -> SystemSettingsService : getSystemSettings()
SystemSettingsService --> WaterDeliveryService : SystemSettings
WaterDeliveryService -> FamilyService : getFamilyById(dto.familyId)
FamilyService --> WaterDeliveryService : Family
WaterDeliveryService -> WaterDeliveryService : distribute water across cisterns
WaterDeliveryService -> FamilyService : save(family)
WaterDeliveryService -> WaterDeliveryRepository : save(WaterDelivery)
WaterDeliveryRepository --> WaterDeliveryService : WaterDelivery
WaterDeliveryService --> WaterDeliveryController : WaterDeliveryDTO
WaterDeliveryController --> User : 201 Created

@enduml
